  <trk>
    <name>Variante Dromaé</name>
    <desc>Dromaé is certainly a place that lies close to the heart of all who live and visit Valle di Ledro. The slightly higher effort required by this additional route compared to the main 729. tour is totally rewarded by its beauty!</desc>
